iiv.data

Class CNUDimensions

  • java.lang.Object
    • iiv.data.CNUDimensions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    iiVScriptable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class CNUDimensions
extends java.lang.Object
implements iiVScriptable, java.lang.Cloneable
    CNUDimensions stores the dimensions of any multidimensional array.
    Since:
    iiV1.0
    See Also:
    CNUData
